><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=aeb656e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=9fbb79eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=f5a51a8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"cadc616c08101610f0f10b6a09e3d5891df96dcd","tid":1670321,"uid":306009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:32:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬衰乜"},{"pid":"31facd6c70c1a738f6ef817a3454bb921715720f","tid":1670321,"uid":258115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b73027835a0b229e8fb251b91a5386c6c1124b","tid":1670321,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e081530cd13e69b7670941193d5ee3230ba99ea","tid":1670321,"uid":2419,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"冇whatsapp定點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:13:17.000Z","msg":"Block撚晒所有聯絡方法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:33:28.000Z","msg":"過一排買張新電話卡 再搵佢傾下"},{"pid":"f52370313d4763629cbbd52efc7e7346e6b3a144","tid":1670321,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"127ce582118aa4f4d08e464a7de3b00d492a068d","tid":1670321,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"我之前同你講既嘢  你可唔可以應承我真係會改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"可以啊屌 可以啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係會改喇 我改咗好多㗎喇<br />\n你俾多次機會我我改埋剩餘個啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets